latestPosts.caption:
Phera of Heeral — My philosophy has always been simple: I want my brides to look like themselves on their most special day, just elevated with grace. Years down the line, when Heeral looks back at these moments, I want her to see her true beauty — not masked by trends or layers of makeup, but enhanced naturally.

This look is all about soft elegance: no heavy lashes, no bold lips, no overpowering base. Just luminous skin, subtle eyes, and a natural flush that reflects the joy of stepping into a new chapter. This is the kind of timeless beauty that never fades.

latestPosts.caption:
For Heeral’s reception look, we went with a glamorous yet elegant vibe to complement her hot pink lehenga and dazzling diamond jewelry. Her eyes were the focal point, featuring a soft smokey blend with a pop of glitter in the center to catch the light just right. We added a flush of rosy blush to bring warmth to her cheeks and finished the look with a pink lipstick that perfectly echoed the vibrant tones of her outfit. The result was a radiant, modern bridal glow that balanced boldness with beauty.
